sections.heading: real estate; sales of twenty-five or more lots
sections.text: Sections 81-885.33 to 81-885.40 shall not apply to sale or lease of real estate not pursuant to a common promotional plan to offer or sell twenty-five or more lots in a subdivision.SourceLaws 1973, LB 68, ยง 42.
